Features
Core Deliverables
View Transactions: Display a table of all transactions.
Add Transaction: Fill out and submit a form to add a new transaction. (Note: This new transaction will only be added to the table and is not persisted to the backend.)
Filter Transactions: Search and filter transactions by description through a search bar.
Bonus Deliverables
Sort Transactions: Sort transactions alphabetically by category or description.
Delete Transactions: Remove a transaction from the table.
