Usage
Viewing Transactions

Upon loading, the application displays a table of all transactions fetched from the JSON server.

Adding Transactions

Use the form provided to enter details of a new transaction and submit it. The transaction will appear in the table but will not be saved to the server.

Filtering Transactions

Type into the search bar to filter transactions by description. Only matching transactions will be displayed.

Sorting Transactions (Bonus)

Use the sorting options to arrange transactions alphabetically by category or description.

Deleting Transactions (Bonus)

Click the delete button associated with a transaction to remove it from the table.

